tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE correlations (
    correlation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    variable1_id INT,
    variable2_id INT,
    correlation_coefficient FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (variable1_id) REFERENCES variables(variable_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (variable2_id) REFERENCES variables(variable_id)
);

CREATE TABLE dataset_variables (
    dataset_variable_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_id INT,
    variable_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (dataset_id) REFERENCES datasets(dataset_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (variable_id) REFERENCES variables(variable_id)
);
